---
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0C447C] mb-4 text-center">Your reasoning, committed to your repo.</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Lodestar captures the thinking behind your code — decisions, dead ends, and direction — and gives you two ways to see it.</p>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">
      <!-- Dashboard screenshot -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-[#185FA5] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Project Dashboard</div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white">
          <img src="/dashboard.png" alt="Lodestar project dashboard showing build status, architecture, and session decisions" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Build status, architecture, decisions — at a glance</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Session context preview -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-[#185FA5] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">What Gets Captured</div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white">
          <div class="p-5 space-y-5">
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0C447C] mb-2">Decisions & Rationale</div>
              <div class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600">
                <div class="pl-3 border-l-2 border-[#185FA5]">
                  <div class="font-medium">Switched from REST to tRPC</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Type safety end-to-end. Simpler DX for a solo founder.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pl-3 border-l-2 border-[#185FA5]">
                  <div class="font-medium">Onboarding: email-first, not social auth</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Devs distrust OAuth popups. Email + magic link converts 2x better.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pl-3 border-l-2 border-[#185FA5]">
                  <div class="font-medium">Ship free tier before Pro</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Trust and adoption matter more than early revenue.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0C447C] mb-2">Dead Ends</div>
              <div class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600">
                <div class="pl-3 border-l-2 border-slate-300">
                  <div class="font-medium">Prisma ORM</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Binary dep caused 2-3s cold starts on Vercel.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pl-3 border-l-2 border-slate-300">
                  <div class="font-medium">Multi-step onboarding wizard</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">40% drop-off at step 2. Replaced with single screen.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0C447C] mb-2">Open Questions</div>
              <div class="space-y-1.5 text-sm">
                <div class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">BLOCKING</span>
                  <span class="text-slate-600">Drizzle push or migrate for production?</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">optional</span>
                  <span class="text-slate-600">Show usage analytics to free users?</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Portable across tools and machines — lives in your repo</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
